text:
@jwrKAS @ronrule Ayar Labs uses silicon photonics to send data as light through fiber:

GPU -- TeraPHY --&gt; Fiber --&gt; TeraPHY -- GPU

optical I/O chiplets can move terabits of data per second with much lower power consumption and latency

